===============================================================================
* chat
===============================================================================
* Created by Laurent Winkler for fun
* Date : January 2009
********************************************************************************

This program creates a chat between two or more workstations. 

usage :

to run the first chat : 

popcrun obj.map ./chat.main

the command to run the second chat is then printed by the program. 

TODO : Avoid conflicts in case of multiple simultaneous connections. 
